# Post creation 

***What kind of content do you want to use***

---
When using this application, users are able to create differents types of content, each type having its own specificities. You can choose the types of content the users will be able to create, we recommand using as much as possible since it brings more ways to interact with other users.

## Types explanations :
### Idea :
An "Idea" content is used to share a simple idea to which users will be able to answer by Yes or No only (This type of card is enabled by default).

### Question :
A "Question" has the same principle than the "Idea" but in this case the user can choose the available answers (This type of card is enabled by default).

### Event :
An "Event" is just an informative card, displaying an information but not waiting for any answers but enables users to applause (This type of card is enabled by default).

### Quote :
A "Quote" is just an informative card, displaying an information but not waiting for any answers.

### Suggestion :
A "Suggestion" is just an informative card, displaying an information but not waiting for any answers.

Each one of these types of content have its own display, adapted to both the cards and list display type, here are some examples:
